      <h1 class="title">Meet the <strong>Beagle</strong></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The Beagle is a small hound known for its <strong>keen sense of smell</strong>
        and a friendly, outgoing personality. It's often described as a
        <em>merry</em> companion, making it a favorite family dog.
      </p>

