    <div id="trivia" class="card">
      <h2 class="section-title">Trivia</h2>
      <ol class="trivia-list">
        <li>
          Beagles are <strong>scent hounds</strong>‚Äîtheir noses are
          exceptionally powerful.
        </li>
        <li>
          The breed is famously <em>vocal</em>, using barks, howls, and the
          classic ‚Äúbay‚Äù.
        </li>
        <li>
          A healthy Beagle weighs about <strong>9-11&nbsp;kg</strong> and stands
          <em>33-41&nbsp;cm</em> at the shoulder (varies by line).
        </li>
        <li>
          Their short coat is <strong>low maintenance</strong>, but they do shed.
        </li>
        <li>
          Beagles are <em>pack-oriented</em> and thrive with regular exercise and
          mental stimulation.
        </li>
      </ol>
